      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal uncertainty propagation through model inputs is not required at MRL 2. Blood rheological properties were taken from published literature values. Sensitivity to viscosity variation was qualitatively assessed and found to have minor influence on hemolysis index predictions."
    },
    {
