      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal test sample characterization beyond what is documented in the FDA benchmark protocol is not required at MRL 2. Bovine blood was used in experiments per the FDA benchmark protocol with documented hematocrit and donor information."
