    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Grid convergence index is well within acceptance threshold. Validation results across all five operating points fall within combined uncertainty bands. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined context of use.",
